  <reign_start rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">274 CE</reign_start>
  <reign_end rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">301 CE</reign_end>
  <significance_si rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">මහාසේන - මින්නේරිය වැව හා ජේතවනාරාමය ඉදිකළ රජු</significance_si>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#Dhatusena">
